@agfero0 , vou fazer uma dessa pra você? 👍
Great pattern! What kind of vinyl do you recommend?

I work as a speech language pathology assistant.  I work with children who need to see my face, especially when I am trying to help them say specific speech sounds. This is the best mask I have found that provides enough coverage for the face, as well as a big window to see the mouth. I know someone previously commented on the vinyl and I am also curious as to what type you used. I would love to use your pattern and attempt to make my own mask for myself and my coworkers. I will make sure to tell them your name because I'm sure mine probably won't turn out as good as yours. (I haven't sewn in years.) Thank you for sharing your designs with us. 😉
👏👏 Thanks for sharing this template! Super useful
